p you create your employee engagement surveys. Go ahead and start creating your surveys! If you have any topics or questions you use in your employee engagement surveys, be sure to share them in the comments below.</p>\n<p><small><a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" title=\"Image inserted by the ImageInject WordPress plugin\" href=\"http://wpinject.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Photo</a> by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/26223114@N02/3777270261\" target=\"_blank\">4nitsirk</a> <a title=\"Attribution-ShareAlike License\" href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-inject/images/cc.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></small></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/creating-employee-engagement-surveys/\">4 Tips For Creating Employee Engagement Surveys</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com\">Quiz And Survey Master</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/creating-employee-engagement-surveys/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"Our Getting Started Workshop\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/our-getting-started-workshop/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 11 Jan 2016 14:15:08 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/?p=4767\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:562:\"<p>Many users have asked for video training or some one-on-one training. I am thrilled to tell you about the workshop I have scheduled this week. Our first online workshop for Quiz And Survey Master, our Getting Started Workshop, is scheduled for 2 PM EST on Wednesday, January 13th and is completely free for all users.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/our-getting-started-workshop/\">Our Getting Started Workshop</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com\">Quiz And Survey Master</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Frank\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1109:\"<p>Many users have asked for video training or some one-on-one training. I am thrilled to tell you about the workshop I have scheduled this week. Our first online workshop for Quiz And Survey Master, our Getting Started Workshop, is scheduled for 2 PM EST on Wednesday, January 13th and is completely free for all users.</p>\n<p>In this workshop, I will be giving an overview of Quiz And Survey Master and will be walking you through many of its features. I will even walk you through creating and setting up quizzes and surveys. There will also be time for questions throughout as well. If you are interested in attending, simply register using the link below and then I&#8217;ll see you at 2 PM EST on January 13th.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/getting-started-register/\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to register for the Getting Started Workshop.</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/our-getting-started-workshop/\">Our Getting Started Workshop</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com\">Quiz And Survey Master</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:8:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"5 Tips For Creating Customer Feedback Surveys\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/collecting-customer-feedback/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/collecting-customer-feedback/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 05 Jan 2016 20:32:29 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:7:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Guides\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"customer\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"example\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"feedback\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"survey\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"user\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/?p=4731\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:479:\"<p>There are a variety of techniques for you to use to get people to take your survey and to maximize the quality of the answers you receive. Check out our tips for creating feedback surveys as well as an example survey.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/collecting-customer-feedback/\">5 Tips For Creating Customer Feedback Surveys</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com\">Quiz And Survey Master</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"script\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:94:\"\n			if (window.qmn_quiz_data === undefined) {\n				window.qmn_quiz_data = new Object();\n			}\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Frank\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18598:\"<p>In a previous post, I discussed how to <a href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/using-quizzes-and-surveys-to-grow-your-mailing-list/\">use surveys to grow your mailing list</a>. Now, once you have started getting users and gaining customers, it is vital to your business to get feedback from them. Customer feedback is crucial to understand what your customers and users think of their experience with your business. Luckily, you can use Quiz And Survey Master to gather feedback! If you have been on <a href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/subscribe-to-our-newsletter/\" target=\"_blank\">our mailing list</a> for a while, you probably have been asked to fill in a survey before about your experience with the plugin. We can then use our user&#8217;s answers to ensure that we are making the right decisions when working on the plugin. I have a few tips for you for creating customer feedback surveys. At the end of this post, you can check out an example survey too.</p>\n<h2>5 Tips for creating customer feedback surveys</h2>\n<p>There are a variety of techniques for you to use to get people to take your survey and to maximize the quality of the answers you receive. Here are a few tips for your surveys:</p>\n<h3>Tell the user how answering the survey will be beneficial</h3>\n<p>When you are asking a user to take the survey, be sure to include why you want them to take the survey and what the answers will help you with. I always include this reason in my email to the user as well as at the beginning of the survey. If users feel that their answers are helping the product that they like, they are more likely to actually take the survey for you.</p>\n<h3>Have a variety of open ended and closed ended questions</h3>\n<p>When you are gathering feedback from your users, you want to be able to quickly look at certain data that you can turn into graphs and compare changes over time. An example would be how responsive your support team is. By making this a closed ended question using a multiple choice question, you can easily graph and compare this data. Furthermore, when you run the feedback survey in the future, you can see how the support team has changed over time. With the <a href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/downloads/results-analysis/\" target=\"_blank\">Reporting &amp; Analysis</a> addon, you can easily see how quantitative answers have changed over time.</p>\n<p>There is also many questions that you will want to be open ended. For example, asking a user why they chose your product is great. However, if you only allowed them to choose from 3 or 4 choices, you may not get the true reasons why your users are choosing your product. You want to use open answer questions to allow you to collect useful qualitative data.</p>\n<h3>Avoid leading questions and giving examples</h3>\n<p>I have come across many surveys that have questions that encourage a particular response. Answers to these questions will lean towards that response and will not accurately relate to the user&#8217;s experience or thoughts. For example, instead of asking &#8220;How good did our burger taste&#8221; which leads the user to &#8220;good&#8221;, ask &#8220;How did our burger taste?&#8221;.</p>\n<p>Also, try to avoid giving example answers as that will also lead users to a particular response. For example, if you asked &#8220;How did you find our website? I.e. Google or Facebook&#8221;, you will find most users will answer Google or Facebook because that was listed. However, if you did not give any examples, you will notice that you have many more unique answers.</p>\n<h3>Keep the survey short</h3>\n<p>There are many questions that you want to ask your users. However, it is best to keep each survey to 7 questions or less. This increases that amount of users that will actually complete your survey. If users come to your survey to find 25 questions, they are very unlikely to complete your survey leaving you with inefficient data. If you have many questions to ask, consider breaking it down to 2 or 3 rounds of surveys over a longer period of time.</p>\n<h3>Consider doing a giveaway</h3>\n<p>To really increase the amount of users that complete your survey, consider doing a promotion or giveaway. I have found that giving a prize to a random user has dramatically increased the amount of users that take the survey if the prize is relevant to your users. For example, you shouldn&#8217;t offer a gift card to a fast food restaurant on a health food site but could consider a gift card to a smoothie restaurant.</p>\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s take a look at an example survey:</p>\n<div class=\'qmn_quiz_container mlw_qmn_quiz\'><form name=\'quizForm17\' id=\'quizForm17\' action=\'\' method=\'post\' class=\'qmn_quiz_form mlw_quiz_form\' novalidate ><div name=\'mlw_error_message\' id=\'mlw_error_message\' class=\'qmn_error_message_section\'></div><span id=\'mlw_top_of_quiz\'></span><div class=\'quiz_section  quiz_begin slide1\'><div class=\'mlw_qmn_message_before\'><p>Welcome to our survey. By completing this survey, you are giving us information to know how to grow and improve upon this plugin. This survey is 7 questions long and will take less than 5 minutes to complete.</p>\n</div><span class=\'mlw_qmn_question\'>Name</span><input type=\'text\' class=\"\" x-webkit-speech name=\'mlwUserName\' value=\'\' /><br /><br /><span class=\'mlw_qmn_question\'>Email</span><input type=\'text\' class=\"mlwEmail\" x-webkit-speech name=\'mlwUserEmail\' value=\'\' /><br /><br /></div><div class=\'quiz_section slide2\'><span class=\'mlw_qmn_question\'>How responsive has our support team been to your questions or concerns?</span><div class=\'qmn_radio_answers mlwRequiredRadio\'><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question122-Extremely responsive\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question122\' id=\'question122_1\' value=\'Extremely responsive\' /> <label for=\'question122_1\'>Extremely responsive</label></div><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question122-Quite responsive\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question122\' id=\'question122_2\' value=\'Quite responsive\' /> <label for=\'question122_2\'>Quite responsive</label></div><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question122-Moderately responsive\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question122\' id=\'question122_3\' value=\'Moderately responsive\' /> <label for=\'question122_3\'>Moderately responsive</label></div><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question122-Slightly responsive\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question122\' id=\'question122_4\' value=\'Slightly responsive\' /> <label for=\'question122_4\'>Slightly responsive</label></div><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question122-Not at all responsive\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question122\' id=\'question122_5\' value=\'Not at all responsive\' /> <label for=\'question122_5\'>Not at all responsive</label></div><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question122-I have never needed support\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question122\' id=\'question122_6\' value=\'I have never needed support\' /> <label for=\'question122_6\'>I have never needed support</label></div><input type=\'radio\' style=\'display: none;\' name=\'question122\' id=\'question122_none\' checked=\'checked\' value=\'No Answer Provided\' /></div></div><br /><div class=\'quiz_section slide3\'><span class=\'mlw_qmn_question\'>How likely are you to recommend this plugin to a friend?</span><div class=\'qmn_radio_answers mlwRequiredRadio\'><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question123-1 - Not at all likely\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question123\' id=\'question123_1\' value=\'1 - Not at all likely\' /> <label for=\'question123_1\'>1 - Not at all likely</label></div><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question123-2\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question123\' id=\'question123_2\' value=\'2\' /> <label for=\'question123_2\'>2</label></div><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question123-3\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question123\' id=\'question123_3\' value=\'3\' /> <label for=\'question123_3\'>3</label></div><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question123-4\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question123\' id=\'question123_4\' value=\'4\' /> <label for=\'question123_4\'>4</label></div><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question123-5\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question123\' id=\'question123_5\' value=\'5\' /> <label for=\'question123_5\'>5</label></div><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question123-6\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question123\' id=\'question123_6\' value=\'6\' /> <label for=\'question123_6\'>6</label></div><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question123-7\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question123\' id=\'question123_7\' value=\'7\' /> <label for=\'question123_7\'>7</label></div><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question123-8\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question123\' id=\'question123_8\' value=\'8\' /> <label for=\'question123_8\'>8</label></div><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question123-9\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question123\' id=\'question123_9\' value=\'9\' /> <label for=\'question123_9\'>9</label></div><div class=\'qmn_mc_answer_wrap\' id=\'question123-10 - Extremely Likely\'><input type=\'radio\' class=\'qmn_quiz_radio\' name=\'question123\' id=\'question123_10\' value=\'10 - Extremely Likely\' /> <label for=\'question123_10\'>10 - Extremely Likely</label></div><input type=\'radio\' style=\'display: none;\' name=\'question123\' id=\'question123_none\' checked=\'checked\' value=\'No Answer Provided\' /></div></div><br /><div class=\'quiz_section slide4\'><span class=\'mlw_qmn_question\'>What led you to look for a quiz or survey plugin? Explain in as much detail as possible how it can make a difference to you.</span><textarea class=\'mlw_answer_open_text mlwRequiredText\' cols=\'70\' rows=\'5\' name=\'question124\' /></textarea></div><br /><div class=\'quiz_section slide5\'><span class=\'mlw_qmn_question\'>What nearly stopped you from using us? List as many items as you can think of.</span><textarea class=\'mlw_answer_open_text mlwRequiredText\' cols=\'70\' rows=\'5\' name=\'question125\' /></textarea></div><br /><div class=\'quiz_section slide6\'><span class=\'mlw_qmn_question\'>What persuaded you to use Quiz And Survey Master. List as many items you can think of.</span><textarea class=\'mlw_answer_open_text mlwRequiredText\' cols=\'70\' rows=\'5\' name=\'question126\' /></textarea></div><br /><div class=\'quiz_section slide7\'><span class=\'mlw_qmn_question\'>What could we have done to make your decision easier?</span><textarea class=\'mlw_answer_open_text mlwRequiredText\' cols=\'70\' rows=\'5\' name=\'question127\' /></textarea></div><br /><div class=\'quiz_section slide8\'><span class=\'mlw_qmn_question\'>How would you describe us to a friend?</span><textarea class=\'mlw_answer_open_text mlwRequiredText\' cols=\'70\' rows=\'5\' name=\'question129\' /></textarea></div><br /><input type=\'hidden\' name=\'qmn_question_list\' value=\'122Q123Q124Q125Q126Q127Q129Q\' /><br /><div class=\'quiz_section slide9 quiz_end\'><input type=\'submit\' class=\'qmn_btn\' value=\'Submit Survey\' /></div><div name=\'mlw_error_message_bottom\' id=\'mlw_error_message_bottom\' class=\'qmn_error_message_section\'></div><input type=\'hidden\' name=\'total_questions\' id=\'total_questions\' value=\'7\'/><input type=\'hidden\' name=\'timer\' id=\'timer\' value=\'0\'/><input type=\'hidden\' class=\'qmn_quiz_id\' name=\'qmn_quiz_id\' id=\'qmn_quiz_id\' value=\'17\'/><input type=\'hidden\' name=\'complete_quiz\' value=\'confirmation\' /></form></div><script>\n			window.qmn_quiz_data[\"17\"] = {\"quiz_id\":\"17\",\"disable_answer\":\"0\",\"ajax_show_correct\":\"0\",\"question_list\":{\"122\":{\"question_id\":\"122\",\"quiz_id\":\"17\",\"question_name\":\"How responsive has our support team been to your questions or concerns?\",\"answer_array\":\"a:6:{i:0;a:3:{i:0;s:20:\\\"Extremely responsive\\\";i:1;d:0;i:2;i:0;}i:1;a:3:{i:0;s:16:\\\"Quite responsive\\\";i:1;d:0;i:2;i:0;}i:2;a:3:{i:0;s:21:\\\"Moderately responsive\\\";i:1;d:0;i:2;i:0;}i:3;a:3:{i:0;s:19:\\\"Slightly responsive\\\";i:1;d:0;i:2;i:0;}i:4;a:3:{i:0;s:21:\\\"Not at all responsive\\\";i:1;d:0;i:2;i:0;}i:5;a:3:{i:0;s:27:\\\"I have never needed support\\\";i:1;d:0;i:2;i:0;}}\",\"answer_one\":\"\",\"answer_one_points\":\"0\",\"answer_two\":\"\",\"answer_two_points\":\"0\",\"answer_three\":\"\",\"answer_three_points\":\"0\",\"answer_four\":\"\",\"answer_four_points\":\"0\",\"answer_five\":\"\",\"answer_five_points\":\"0\",\"answer_six\":\"\",\"answer_six_points\":\"0\",\"correct_answer\":\"0\",\"question_answer_info\":\"\",\"comments\":\"1\",\"hints\":\"\",\"question_order\":\"1\",\"question_type\":\"0\",\"question_type_new\":\"0\",\"question_settings\":\"a:1:{s:8:\\\"required\\\";i:0;}\",\"category\":\"\",\"deleted\":\"0\",\"answers\":[[\"Extremely responsive\",0,0],