veryone! Now that we are into the 4th quarter of the year, now is a great time to review the status of Quiz And Survey Master and to make sure that the direction I am taking it aligns with what the users need. As such, I have put together a 4th quarter survey so I [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/need-some-feedback-4th-quarter-survey/\">Need Some Feedback &#8211; 4th Quarter Survey</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com\">Quiz And Survey Master</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Frank\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1073:\"<p>Hey everyone! Now that we are into the 4th quarter of the year, now is a great time to review the status of Quiz And Survey Master and to make sure that the direction I am taking it aligns with what the users need. As such, I have put together a 4th quarter survey so I can see how people are using the plugin. The survey is only 9 questions long and will take you less than 5 minutes to complete. Please complete this survey so I can make sure that the current plans align with what the users want and need. This survey is only active until October 30th, so please take this survey right away.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/quiz/survey/\" target=\"_blank\">Click to take survey now.</a></p>\n<p>As always, thank you for being a part of the Quiz And Survey Master community.</p>\n<p>~Frank</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://quizandsurveymaster.com/need-some-feedback-4th-quarter-survey/\">Need Some Feedback &#8211; 4th Quarter Survey</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" hr