http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/24235d4fd920fecd4aaae64b7f947c02_-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"24235d4fd920fecd4aaae64b7f947c02_\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-120\" src=\"http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d80aa675ed27e3b65dad3a64db5544c4_-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"d80aa675ed27e3b65dad3a64db5544c4_\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-121\" src=\"http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/fb2d093acb0bc689b683b81b644f023d_-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"fb2d093acb0bc689b683b81b644f023d_\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />','曙光里夏游怀柔','','inherit','closed','closed','','115-revision-v1','','','2016-05-24 15:30:18','2016-05-24 07:30:18','',115,'http://101.200.160.181/microlele/2016/05/24/115-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(123,2,'2016-05-25 15:17:55','2016-05-25 07:17:55','<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><b>             </b>——优雅浑然天成</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">       2016年5月23日，由北京善韵文化艺术发展有限公司和北京慧姗姗科技发展有限公司共同组织的旗袍文化讲座，在曙光里苏宁电器三楼教室的活动厅举办，主题为“旗袍文化，旗袍的日常穿搭”，由徐冬老师演讲。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">        徐冬老师，满族人，研究旗袍文化20年，对旗袍十分热衷，对旗袍的文化也相当了解，老师最近工作主要针对各大院校，比如北大、清华等进行演讲，希望能让年轻人更多的了解旗袍并发展下去。这次有幸请到徐冬老师来社区演讲，各位来到现场的老年人十分活跃和开心。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-149 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464073664031_59-122x300.png\" alt=\"filehelper_1464073664031_59\" width=\"122\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">         为了让大家消除对旗袍只能身材好的人在特定场合才能穿的想法，老师穿了一件旗袍，并用一个外套进行搭配，大方、美丽，合身而且特别舒服。而且老师特意做了 PPT为大家讲述旗袍的由来和发展史。最后，老师和老人一起互动，研究旗袍的穿法，还带了一些老师设计的旗袍让老人们试穿，让大家明白老年人也可以穿旗 袍，不管年龄、场合、身材，都可以通过旗袍来体现中国女性的美。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">       老师为老人们讲课。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-141\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464143944500_97-257x300.jpg\" alt=\"filehelper_1464143944500_97\" width=\"257\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-142\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464143944515_18-257x300.jpg\" alt=\"filehelper_1464143944515_18\" width=\"257\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-136\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464143944390_62-257x300.jpg\" alt=\"filehelper_1464143944390_62\" width=\"257\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-139\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464143944453_70-257x300.jpg\" alt=\"filehelper_1464143944453_70\" width=\"257\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-138\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464143944437_76-257x300.jpg\" alt=\"filehelper_1464143944437_76\" width=\"257\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">老师为大家示范旗袍的讲究，比如穿法、站姿、坐姿等。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">  <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-147\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464143957937_25-257x300.jpg\" alt=\"filehelper_1464143957937_25\" width=\"257\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-143\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464143944546_5-257x300.jpg\" alt=\"filehelper_1464143944546_5\" width=\"257\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">老人根据自己对旗袍的想法进行演讲。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-148\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464143957968_74-257x300.jpg\" alt=\"filehelper_1464143957968_74\" width=\"257\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">老师为老人们带来自己设计的旗袍向大家展示。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-134\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464143944328_50-257x300.jpg\" alt=\"filehelper_1464143944328_50\" width=\"257\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">老人们为大家示范老师带来的旗袍，穿上旗袍，大家都仿佛看到年轻的自己，各种摆姿势拍照。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-144\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464143957875_15-257x300.jpg\" alt=\"filehelper_1464143957875_15\" width=\"257\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-140\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464143944484_77-257x300.jpg\" alt=\"filehelper_1464143944484_77\" width=\"257\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-137\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464143944406_42-257x300.jpg\" alt=\"filehelper_1464143944406_42\" width=\"257\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">还有老人带来自己年轻时期穿的旗袍，向老师咨询穿搭方式。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-146\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464143957921_66-257x300.jpg\" alt=\"filehelper_1464143957921_66\" width=\"257\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-135\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464143944359_37-257x300.jpg\" alt=\"filehelper_1464143944359_37\" width=\"257\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n\n\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">更多精彩内容敬请关注老友资讯公众微信号。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-164\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/233663652699833315-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"233663652699833315\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>','曙光里旗袍文化，旗袍的日常穿搭','','inherit','closed','closed','','47-autosave-v1','','','2016-05-25 15:17:55','2016-05-25 07:17:55','',47,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/2016/05/24/47-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(124,2,'2016-05-24 16:58:16','2016-05-24 08:58:16','<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><b></b><strong><b>   </b></strong>     ——优雅浑然天成</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n2016年5月23日，由北京善韵文化艺术发展有限公司和北京慧姗姗科技发展有限公司共同组织的旗袍文化讲座，在曙光里苏宁电器三楼教室的活动厅举办，主题为“旗袍文化，旗袍的日常穿搭”，由徐冬老师演讲。\r\n\r\n徐冬老师，满族人，研究旗袍文化20年，对旗袍十分热衷，对旗袍的文化也相当了解，老师最近工作主要针对各大院校，比如北大、清华等进行演讲，希望能让年轻人更多的了解旗袍并发展下去。这次有幸请到徐冬老师来社区演讲，各位来到现场的老年人十分活跃和开心。\r\n\r\n为了让大家消除对旗袍只能身材好的人在特定场合才能穿的想法，老师穿了一件旗袍，并用一个外套进行搭配，大方、美丽，合身而且特别舒服。而且老师特意做了PPT为大家讲述旗袍的由来和发展史。最后，老师和老人一起互动，研究旗袍的穿法，还带了一些老师设计的旗袍让老人们试穿，让大家明白老年人也可以穿旗袍，不管年龄、场合、身材，都可以通过旗袍来体现中国女性的美。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-98 alignleft\" src=\"http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/filehelper_1464073664031_59-122x300.png\" alt=\"filehelper_1464073664031_59\" width=\"122\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-76\" src=\"http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/382477557108272396-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"382477557108272396\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-74\" src=\"http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/328045336378163641-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"328045336378163641\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-73\" src=\"http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/313112453229195086-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"313112453229195086\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-87\" src=\"http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/685406789348448222-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"685406789348448222\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-92\" src=\"http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/791657964641589170-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"791657964641589170\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-69\" src=\"http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/143100285156321552-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"143100285156321552\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-72\" src=\"http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/199083212555262010-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"199083212555262010\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-84\" src=\"http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/652440277825140980-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"652440277825140980\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-97\" src=\"http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/809523553556667190-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"809523553556667190\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-91\" src=\"http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/788111229207442692-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"788111229207442692\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-90\" src=\"http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/743788968608527419-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"743788968608527419\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-70\" src=\"http://101.200.160.181/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/157504575158589130-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"157504575158589130\" width=\"225\" heig