'','d355e5757ee3a5733c1-2','','','2016-05-26 18:05:18','2016-05-26 10:05:18','',192,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757ee3a5733c1-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(204,3,'2016-05-26 18:05:33','2016-05-26 10:05:33','','d355e5757eecd173371','','inherit','open','closed','','d355e5757eecd173371','','','2016-05-26 18:05:33','2016-05-26 10:05:33','',192,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757eecd173371.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(205,3,'2016-05-26 18:05:38','2016-05-26 10:05:38','','d355e57579a53d53731','','inherit','open','closed','','d355e57579a53d53731','','','2016-05-26 18:05:38','2016-05-26 10:05:38','',192,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579a53d53731.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(206,3,'2016-05-26 18:05:44','2016-05-26 10:05:44','','d355e57579aade53d51','','inherit','open','closed','','d355e57579aade53d51','','','2016-05-26 18:05:44','2016-05-26 10:05:44','',192,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579aade53d51.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(207,3,'2016-05-26 18:05:49','2016-05-26 10:05:49','','d355e57579abed93d91','','inherit','open','closed','','d355e57579abed93d91','','','2016-05-26 18:05:49','2016-05-26 10:05:49','',192,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579abed93d91.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(208,3,'2016-05-26 18:05:56','2016-05-26 10:05:56','','d355e57579ae7973791','','inherit','open','closed','','d355e57579ae7973791','','','2016-05-26 18:05:56','2016-05-26 10:05:56','',192,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579ae7973791.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(209,3,'2016-05-26 18:06:02','2016-05-26 10:06:02','','d355e5757911cc93ec1','','inherit','open','closed','','d355e5757911cc93ec1','','','2016-05-26 18:06:02','2016-05-26 10:06:02','',192,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757911cc93ec1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(210,3,'2016-05-26 18:06:28','2016-05-26 10:06:28','','d355e5757e9553735d1','','inherit','open','closed','','d355e5757e9553735d1','','','2016-05-26 18:06:28','2016-05-26 10:06:28','',192,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e9553735d1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(211,3,'2016-05-26 18:14:00','2016-05-26 10:14:00','都说女儿是妈妈的小棉袄，但是再贴心都会有出嫁那一天，老妈们难免会不舍并难以释怀，暂时先过滤掉吧，想想女儿找到了自己的幸福成立了家庭应该是值得庆祝和高兴的事情，在她一生中最重要的日子里，她一定希望你美美的做她的婚礼见证人并能听到你的祝福。但妈妈们在女儿的婚礼上穿什么礼服最合适最好看呢，还是有必要提前准备一下的，看看13位国外老妈是怎么搞定的吧<strong>。</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-203\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757ee3a5733c1-1-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757ee3a5733c1\" width=\"268\" height=\"396\" />\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                                      Killian</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿粉色蕾丝修身连衣裙</span>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">Killian</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的婚礼在加利福尼亚的丽思卡尔顿酒店举行，她身着白色<span lang=\"EN-US\">V</span>领蕾丝婚纱，她的妈妈身穿粉色蕾丝修身连衣裙宛如少女，母女俩像极了姐妹花，近乎一样的面容，同是纤细高挑的身材，礼服上的蕾丝细节等等，两人浑身上下都透着不俗的品味。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">                                                                                                        <img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-204\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757eecd173371-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757eecd173371\" width=\"284\" height=\"420\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                                       Lauren</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿金色亮片薄纱长裙</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Michael</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Lauren</span>在英国乡间举办的婚礼竟然布置的如此奢华隆重，场面一点不输皇室婚礼。<span lang=\"EN-US\">Lauren</span>身穿抹胸薄纱婚纱头戴水晶发饰，就跟公主出嫁如出一辙。她帮母亲选择了一件优雅的金色亮片薄纱长裙，既高贵范儿又颇具时尚感。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">                                                                                                         <img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-202\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e939773531-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e939773531\" width=\"272\" height=\"402\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                     Jessica</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿渐变绿色<span lang=\"EN-US\">V</span>领连衣裙搭配蓝色披风</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Matthew</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jessica</span>的婚礼选在威雷亚四季度假村举行，浪漫的夏威夷风迎面扑来。新娘和父母一起沿着过道走完整个户外仪式，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jessica</span>的母亲身穿渐变绿色<span lang=\"EN-US\">V</span>领连衣裙搭配蓝色披风，这样的搭配似乎使我们嗅到了太平洋深海的气息。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\">                                                                                  <img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-198\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e9cda135c1-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e9cda135c1\" width=\"241\" height=\"356\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">Mallorie</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿金亮片单肩薄纱长礼服</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Dan</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mallorie</span>的婚礼在纽约的埃塞克斯之家举行，婚礼现场极尽奢华，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mallorie</span>的妈妈身穿金亮片单肩薄纱长礼服，高贵极了。虽然<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mallorie</span>身上的<span lang=\"EN-US\">Monique Lhuillier</span>舞会婚纱聚焦了整个中心舞台，但依然没有夺去妈妈的光芒。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-210\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e9553735d1-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e9553735d1\" width=\"254\" height=\"380\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">Sarah</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿黑色薄纱礼服</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Scott</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Sarah</span>的婚礼选择在纽约市一个华丽的大学俱乐部里举行，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Sarah</span>的妈妈身穿黑色薄纱礼服搭配同色披风，高贵又典雅。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-201\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e9ddb935e1-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e9ddb935e1\" width=\"253\" height=\"374\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">Anna</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的母亲身穿蓝色蕾丝及膝礼裙</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Akshay</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Anna</span>的婚礼选在了布朗克斯动物园举行，那个充满宝石色调和印度风格的场地正是他们想要的，他们的婚礼是优雅和特殊的，也是轻松和舒适的。<span lang=\"EN-US\">Anna</span>的母亲身穿蓝色蕾丝及膝礼裙站在女儿身旁，无论从身材还是衣品来说，都丝毫不输新娘子。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-199\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e9ea333da1-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e9ea333da1\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">Danielle</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿淡蓝色斜纹软呢连衣裙</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jonathon</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Danielle</span>的婚礼在历史文化悠久的洛雷斯天主教堂举行，而婚礼来宾接待处选在了旧金山的亚洲艺术博物馆。两个地方都很复古高贵，风格很周董。<span lang=\"EN-US\">Danielle</span>的妈妈身穿一件淡蓝色斜纹软呢连衣裙，外搭米色雪纺外套，优雅极了。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-200\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e99c373d31-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e99c373d31\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">Theresa</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿灰色波点薄纱领长裙</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Sven</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Theresa</span>选择了风景如画的哥斯达黎加海滩作为婚礼举办地，这么美的地方一定会让人感受到前有未有的惬意与愉悦。<span lang=\"EN-US\">Theresa</span>的母亲很应景的穿上了灰色波点薄纱领长裙，视觉画面上增添了飘逸感。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-206\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579aade53d51-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e57579aade53d51\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">Karine</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿紫色低领连衣裙</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Carl</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Karine</span>的婚礼选择在科罗拉多溢出风景优美的室外园林举行，所有的男嘉宾都身着西服上衣搭配格子短裙，十分苏格兰风情。<span lang=\"EN-US\">Karine</span>的妈妈身着紫色低领连衣裙，风韵犹存。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-207\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579abed93d91-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e57579abed93d91\" width=\"293\" height=\"433\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">Jonie</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿裸色露肩连衣裙</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Brad</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jonie</span>在加利福尼亚举行了一个浪漫的户外婚礼，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jonie</span>的妈妈选择了一件裸色露肩连衣裙，淡柔的颜色很符合妈妈的风格。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-205\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579a53d53731-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e57579a53d53731\" width=\"288\" height=\"425\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">Besse</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿白色套装内搭红色抹胸内衣</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Michael</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Besse</span>的婚礼选在一个葡萄酒庄园里举行，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Besse</span>身着<span lang=\"EN-US\">Saks Fifth Avenue</span>白色吊带婚纱，这件婚纱也可以算是古董了，她妈妈在<span lang=\"EN-US\">1979</span>年一个晚宴上就曾穿过。而今天在女儿的婚礼上，她和<span lang=\"EN-US\">Besse</span>的爸爸穿着都较为休闲，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Besse</span>的妈妈一袭白色套装内搭红色抹胸内衣。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-208\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579ae7973791-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e57579ae7973791\" width=\"264\" height=\"390\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">Karin</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿香槟色深<span lang=\"EN-US\">V</span>短裙搭配同色外套</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Billy</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Karin</span>在加利福尼亚州的欧海举行了一个充满生机的春天婚礼，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Karin</span>的母亲身穿香槟色深<span lang=\"EN-US\">V</span>短裙搭配同色外套，既性感迷人又极显气质。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-209\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757911cc93ec1-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757911cc93ec1\" width=\"265\" height=\"392\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">Garrick</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿淡绿色多层连衣裙搭配披风</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Dare</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Garrick</span>的婚礼在加州纳帕的卡内罗斯客栈举行，新郎的妈妈和新娘的妈妈很可爱的同时出现在一个画面里，她们都身着橘色和淡绿色多层连衣裙，搭配披风，活力十足很显年轻。</span></p>','13位老妈有话说 女儿结婚她们穿这些礼服最好看','','inherit','closed','closed','','192-revision-v1','','','2016-05-26 18:14:00','2016-05-26 10:14:00','',192,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/2016/05/26/192-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(213,3,'2016-05-26 18:21:16','2016-05-26 10:21:16','','7L]FFO}3$KMH`XQ5W${`69O','','inherit','open','closed','','7lffo3kmhxq5w69o','','','2016-05-26 18:21:16','2016-05-26 10:21:16','',192,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/7LFFO3KMHXQ5W69O.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(214,3,'2016-05-26 18:24:41','2016-05-26 10:24:41','都说女儿是妈妈的小棉袄，但是再贴心都会有出嫁那一天，老妈们难免会不舍并难以释怀，暂时先过滤掉吧，想想女儿找到了自己的幸福成立了家庭应该是值得庆祝和高兴的事情，在她一生中最重要的日子里，她一定希望你美美的做她的婚礼见证人并能听到你的祝福。但妈妈们在女儿的婚礼上穿什么礼服最合适最好看呢，还是有必要提前准备一下的，看看13位国外老妈是怎么搞定的吧<strong>。</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-203\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757ee3a5733c1-1-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757ee3a5733c1\" width=\"268\" height=\"396\" />\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                                      Killian</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿粉色蕾丝修身连衣裙</span>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">Killian</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的婚礼在加利福尼亚的丽思卡尔顿酒店举行，她身着白色<span lang=\"EN-US\">V</span>领蕾丝婚纱，她的妈妈身穿粉色蕾丝修身连衣裙宛如少女，母女俩像极了姐妹花，近乎一样的面容，同是纤细高挑的身材，礼服上的蕾丝细节等等，两人浑身上下都透着不俗的品味。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">                                                                                                        <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-204\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757eecd173371-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757eecd173371\" width=\"284\" height=\"420\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                                       Lauren</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿金色亮片薄纱长裙</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Michael</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Lauren</span>在英国乡间举办的婚礼竟然布置的如此奢华隆重，场面一点不输皇室婚礼。<span lang=\"EN-US\">Lauren</span>身穿抹胸薄纱婚纱头戴水晶发饰，就跟公主出嫁如出一辙。她帮母亲选择了一件优雅的金色亮片薄纱长裙，既高贵范儿又颇具时尚感。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">                                                                                                         <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-202\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e939773531-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e939773531\" width=\"272\" height=\"402\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                     Jessica</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿渐变绿色<span lang=\"EN-US\">V</span>领连衣裙搭配蓝色披风</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Matthew</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jessica</span>的婚礼选在威雷亚四季度假村举行，浪漫的夏威夷风迎面扑来。新娘和父母一起沿着过道走完整个户外仪式，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jessica</span>的母亲身穿渐变绿色<span lang=\"EN-US\">V</span>领连衣裙搭配蓝色披风，这样的搭配似乎使我们嗅到了太平洋深海的气息。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\">                                                                                           <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-198\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e9cda135c1-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e9cda135c1\" width=\"294\" height=\"435\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                            Mallorie</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿金亮片单肩薄纱长礼服</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Dan</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mallorie</span>的婚礼在纽约的埃塞克斯之家举行，婚礼现场极尽奢华，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mallorie</span>的妈妈身穿金亮片单肩薄纱长礼服，高贵极了。虽然<span lang=\"EN-US\">Mallorie</span>身上的<span lang=\"EN-US\">Monique Lhuillier</span>舞会婚纱聚焦了整个中心舞台，但依然没有夺去妈妈的光芒。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\">                                                                                             <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-210\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e9553735d1-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e9553735d1\" width=\"309\" height=\"464\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                                     Sarah</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿黑色薄纱礼服</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Scott</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Sarah</span>的婚礼选择在纽约市一个华丽的大学俱乐部里举行，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Sarah</span>的妈妈身穿黑色薄纱礼服搭配同色披风，高贵又典雅。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\">                                                                                             <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-201\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e9ddb935e1-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e9ddb935e1\" width=\"310\" height=\"458\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                                  Anna</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的母亲身穿蓝色蕾丝及膝礼裙</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Akshay</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Anna</span>的婚礼选在了布朗克斯动物园举行，那个充满宝石色调和印度风格的场地正是他们想要的，他们的婚礼是优雅和特殊的，也是轻松和舒适的。<span lang=\"EN-US\">Anna</span>的母亲身穿蓝色蕾丝及膝礼裙站在女儿身旁，无论从身材还是衣品来说，都丝毫不输新娘子。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\">                                                                                              <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-199\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e9ea333da1-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e9ea333da1\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                              Danielle</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿淡蓝色斜纹软呢连衣裙</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jonathon</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Danielle</span>的婚礼在历史文化悠久的洛雷斯天主教堂举行，而婚礼来宾接待处选在了旧金山的亚洲艺术博物馆。两个地方都很复古高贵，风格很周董。<span lang=\"EN-US\">Danielle</span>的妈妈身穿一件淡蓝色斜纹软呢连衣裙，外搭米色雪纺外套，优雅极了。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\">                                                                                                <img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-200\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e99c373d31-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e99c373d31\" width=\"313\" height=\"313\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                                 Theresa</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿灰色波点薄纱领长裙</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Sven</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Theresa</span>选择了风景如画的哥斯达黎加海滩作为婚礼举办地，这么美的地方一定会让人感受到前有未有的惬意与愉悦。<span lang=\"EN-US\">Theresa</span>的母亲很应景的穿上了灰色波点薄纱领长裙，视觉画面上增添了飘逸感。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\">                                                                                                 <img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-206\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579aade53d51-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e57579aade53d51\" width=\"323\" height=\"323\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                                        Karine</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿紫色低领连衣裙</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Carl</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Karine</span>的婚礼选择在科罗拉多溢出风景优美的室外园林举行，所有的男嘉宾都身着西服上衣搭配格子短裙，十分苏格兰风情。<span lang=\"EN-US\">Karine</span>的妈妈身着紫色低领连衣裙，风韵犹存。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\">                                                                                                  <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-207\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579abed93d91-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e57579abed93d91\" width=\"327\" height=\"483\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                                       Jonie</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿裸色露肩连衣裙</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Brad</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jonie</span>在加利福尼亚举行了一个浪漫的户外婚礼，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jonie</span>的妈妈选择了一件裸色露肩连衣裙，淡柔的颜色很符合妈妈的风格。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\">                                                                                                  <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-205\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579a53d53731-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e57579a53d53731\" width=\"324\" height=\"479\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                                 Besse</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿白色套装内搭红色抹胸内衣</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Michael</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Besse</span>的婚礼选在一个葡萄酒庄园里举行，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Besse</span>身着<span lang=\"EN-US\">Saks Fifth Avenue</span>白色吊带婚纱，这件婚纱也可以算是古董了，她妈妈在<span lang=\"EN-US\">1979</span>年一个晚宴上就曾穿过。而今天在女儿的婚礼上，她和<span lang=\"EN-US\">Besse</span>的爸爸穿着都较为休闲，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Besse</span>的妈妈一袭白色套装内搭红色抹胸内衣。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\">                                                                                                 <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-208\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579ae7973791-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e57579ae7973791\" width=\"331\" height=\"489\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                                Karin</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿香槟色深<span lang=\"EN-US\">V</span>短裙搭配同色外套</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Billy</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Karin</span>在加利福尼亚州的欧海举行了一个充满生机的春天婚礼，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Karin</span>的母亲身穿香槟色深<span lang=\"EN-US\">V</span>短裙搭配同色外套，既性感迷人又极显气质。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\">                                                                                                <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-209\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757911cc93ec1-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757911cc93ec1\" width=\"341\" height=\"504\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">                                                                               Garrick</span><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">的妈妈身穿淡绿色多层连衣裙搭配披风</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\"><span style=\"font-family: \'微软雅黑\',\'sans-serif\';color: #222222\">新郎<span lang=\"EN-US\">Dare</span>和新娘<span lang=\"EN-US\">Garrick</span>的婚礼在加州纳帕的卡内罗斯客栈举行，新郎的妈妈和新娘的妈妈很可爱的同时出现在一个画面里，她们都身着橘色和淡绿色多层连衣裙，搭配披风，活力十足很显年轻。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\">                                                                                                                                <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/7LFFO3KMHXQ5W69O.png\" alt=\"7L]FFO}3$KMH&#096;XQ5W${&#096;69O\" width=\"84\" height=\"84\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-indent: 24pt;line-height: 24pt;margin: 9pt 0cm;text-align: left;background: white\">                                                                                    <strong>长按上方二维码点击关注，获得更多中老年时尚服装咨询</strong></h4>','13位老妈有话说 女儿结婚她们穿这些礼服最好看','','inherit','closed','closed','','192-revision-v1','','','2016-05-26 18:24:41','2016-05-26 10:24:41','',192,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/2016/05/26/192-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(215,3,'2016-05-27 09:54:36','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','自动草稿','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-05-27 09:54:36','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/?p=215',0,'post','',0),(216,3,'2016-05-27 10:09:08','2016-05-27 02:09:08','都说女儿是妈妈的小棉袄，但是再贴心都会有出嫁那一天，老妈们难免会不舍并难以释怀，暂时先过滤掉吧，想想女儿找到了自己的幸福成立了家庭应该是值得庆祝和高兴的事情，在她一生中最重要的日子里，她一定希望你美美的做她的婚礼见证人并能听到你的祝福。但妈妈们在女儿的婚礼上穿什么礼服最合适最好看呢，还是有必要提前准备一下的，看看13位国外老妈是怎么搞定的吧。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-203\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757ee3a5733c1-1-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757ee3a5733c1\" width=\"271\" height=\"400\" />\r\n\r\nKillian的妈妈身穿粉色蕾丝修身连衣裙\r\n\r\nKillian的婚礼在加利福尼亚的丽思卡尔顿酒店举行，她身着白色V领蕾丝婚纱，她的妈妈身穿粉色蕾丝修身连衣裙宛如少女，母女俩像极了姐妹花，近乎一样的面容，同是纤细高挑的身材，礼服上的蕾丝细节等等，两人浑身上下都透着不俗的品味。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-204\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757eecd173371-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757eecd173371\" width=\"270\" height=\"399\" />\r\n\r\nLauren的妈妈身穿金色亮片薄纱长裙\r\n\r\n新郎Michael和新娘Lauren在英国乡间举办的婚礼竟然布置的如此奢华隆重，场面一点不输皇室婚礼。Lauren身穿抹胸薄纱婚纱头戴水晶发饰，就跟公主出嫁如出一辙。她帮母亲选择了一件优雅的金色亮片薄纱长裙，既高贵范儿又颇具时尚感。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-202\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e939773531-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e939773531\" width=\"266\" height=\"393\" />\r\n\r\nJessica的妈妈身穿渐变绿色V领连衣裙搭配蓝色披风\r\n\r\n新郎Matthew和新娘Jessica的婚礼选在威雷亚四季度假村举行，浪漫的夏威夷风迎面扑来。新娘和父母一起沿着过道走完整个户外仪式，Jessica的母亲身穿渐变绿色V领连衣裙搭配蓝色披风，这样的搭配似乎使我们嗅到了太平洋深海的气息。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-198\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e9cda135c1-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e9cda135c1\" width=\"267\" height=\"395\" />\r\n\r\nMallorie的妈妈身穿金亮片单肩薄纱长礼服\r\n\r\n新郎Dan和新娘Mallorie的婚礼在纽约的埃塞克斯之家举行，婚礼现场极尽奢华，Mallorie的妈妈身穿金亮片单肩薄纱长礼服，高贵极了。虽然Mallorie身上的Monique Lhuillier舞会婚纱聚焦了整个中心舞台，但依然没有夺去妈妈的光芒。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-210\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e9553735d1-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e9553735d1\" width=\"268\" height=\"402\" />\r\n\r\nSarah的妈妈身穿黑色薄纱礼服\r\n\r\n新郎Scott和新娘Sarah的婚礼选择在纽约市一个华丽的大学俱乐部里举行，Sarah的妈妈身穿黑色薄纱礼服搭配同色披风，高贵又典雅。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-201\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e9ddb935e1-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e9ddb935e1\" width=\"270\" height=\"399\" />\r\n\r\nAnna的母亲身穿蓝色蕾丝及膝礼裙\r\n\r\n新郎Akshay和新娘Anna的婚礼选在了布朗克斯动物园举行，那个充满宝石色调和印度风格的场地正是他们想要的，他们的婚礼是优雅和特殊的，也是轻松和舒适的。Anna的母亲身穿蓝色蕾丝及膝礼裙站在女儿身旁，无论从身材还是衣品来说，都丝毫不输新娘子。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-199\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e9ea333da1-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e9ea333da1\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\nDanielle的妈妈身穿淡蓝色斜纹软呢连衣裙\r\n\r\n新郎Jonathon和新娘Danielle的婚礼在历史文化悠久的洛雷斯天主教堂举行，而婚礼来宾接待处选在了旧金山的亚洲艺术博物馆。两个地方都很复古高贵，风格很周董。Danielle的妈妈身穿一件淡蓝色斜纹软呢连衣裙，外搭米色雪纺外套，优雅极了。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-200\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757e99c373d31-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757e99c373d31\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\nTheresa的妈妈身穿灰色波点薄纱领长裙\r\n\r\n新郎Sven和新娘Theresa选择了风景如画的哥斯达黎加海滩作为婚礼举办地，这么美的地方一定会让人感受到前有未有的惬意与愉悦。Theresa的母亲很应景的穿上了灰色波点薄纱领长裙，视觉画面上增添了飘逸感。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-206\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579aade53d51-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e57579aade53d51\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\nKarine的妈妈身穿紫色低领连衣裙\r\n\r\n新郎Carl和新娘Karine的婚礼选择在科罗拉多溢出风景优美的室外园林举行，所有的男嘉宾都身着西服上衣搭配格子短裙，十分苏格兰风情。Karine的妈妈身着紫色低领连衣裙，风韵犹存。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-207\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579abed93d91-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e57579abed93d91\" width=\"288\" height=\"426\" />\r\nJonie的妈妈身穿裸色露肩连衣裙\r\n\r\n新郎Brad和新娘Jonie在加利福尼亚举行了一个浪漫的户外婚礼，Jonie的妈妈选择了一件裸色露肩连衣裙，淡柔的颜色很符合妈妈的风格。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-205\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579a53d53731-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e57579a53d53731\" width=\"293\" height=\"433\" />\r\nBesse的妈妈身穿白色套装内搭红色抹胸内衣\r\n\r\n新郎Michael和新娘Besse的婚礼选在一个葡萄酒庄园里举行，Besse身着Saks Fifth Avenue白色吊带婚纱，这件婚纱也可以算是古董了，她妈妈在1979年一个晚宴上就曾穿过。而今天在女儿的婚礼上，她和Besse的爸爸穿着都较为休闲，Besse的妈妈一袭白色套装内搭红色抹胸内衣。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-208\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e57579ae7973791-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e57579ae7973791\" width=\"293\" height=\"433\" />\r\n\r\nKarin的妈妈身穿香槟色深V短裙搭配同色外套\r\n\r\n新郎Billy和新娘Karin在加利福尼亚州的欧海举行了一个充满生机的春天婚礼，Karin的母亲身穿香槟色深V短裙搭配同色外套，既性感迷人又极显气质。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-209\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/d355e5757911cc93ec1-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"d355e5757911cc93ec1\" width=\"296\" height=\"437\" />\r\n\r\nGarrick的妈妈身穿淡绿色多层连衣裙搭配披风\r\n\r\n新郎Dare和新娘Garrick的婚礼在加州纳帕的卡内罗斯客栈举行，新郎的妈妈和新娘的妈妈很可爱的同时出现在一个画面里，她们都身着橘色和淡绿色多层连衣裙，搭配披风，活力十足很显年轻。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/7LFFO3KMHXQ5W69O.png\" alt=\"7L]FFO}3$KMH&#096;XQ5W${&#096;69O\" width=\"84\" height=\"84\" />\r\n\r\n长按上方二维码点击关注，获得更多中老年时尚服装咨询','13位老妈有话说 女儿结婚她们穿这些礼服最好看','','inherit','closed','closed','','192-revision-v1','','','2016-05-27 10:09:08','2016-05-27 02:09:08','',192,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/2016/05/27/192-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(217,3,'2016-05-27 10:20:09','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','自动草稿','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-05-27 10:20:09','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/?p=217',0,'post','',0),(218,3,'2016-05-27 10:20:33','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','自动草稿','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-05-27 10:20:33','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/?p=218',0,'post','',0),(219,3,'2016-05-27 10:20:37','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','自动草稿','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-05-27 10:20:37','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/?p=219',0,'post','',0),(220,3,'2016-05-27 10:20:46','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','自动草稿','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-05-27 10:20:46','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/?p=220',0,'post','',0),(221,3,'2016-05-27 10:50:18','2016-05-27 02:50:18','很多老年人在选择夏天穿的衣服时多半会考虑面料问题，但是真正依据科学判断的并不多，很多老年人以经验之谈选购服装，最后穿着起来未必舒适和凉快。今天，就来给大家普及一下知识：老年人应该从哪几个方面入手来选择夏季服装的面料。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-222\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/2015032809320584-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"2015032809320584\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" />\r\n(1) 吸湿性：当气温达到30摄氏度左右时，人体就会大量出汗。因为气温接近或超过体温时，人体散热主要靠汗液的蒸发。烈日炎炎的夏天，人体每小时 可散发500—1000毫升的汗液。夏季服装是否凉爽与衣料的吸湿性有密切关系，吸湿性能好的布料，可将汗液迅速及时吸出后蒸发掉，于是就显得很凉快 。吸湿性能差的衣料，即使很薄很光，也照样汗流浃背，闷热难受。\r\n不同的布料吸湿性相差很大，据测定，气温在24摄氏度时，相对湿度为50％-70％时，人造粘胶纤维吸湿率为10％-14％，蚕丝织品为8％-1 1％，棉织品 为6％-9％，亚麻为8.3％-11.7％ ，维纶为3％，涤纶不足1％。夏天即使穿很薄、孔隙很大的尼龙衫也很闷热，其原因是尼龙属于合成纤维，吸湿性最差。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-223\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Fq6kZVPQN0SjeUtL6QQza4I3Tx-Z-300x188.png\" alt=\"Fq6kZVPQN0SjeUtL6QQza4I3Tx-Z\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\" />\r\n\r\n(2) 透气性：衣料的透气性能取决于纺织的密度。纺织品的密度越高，透气性能越差，密度越低透气性能越好。同样原料织成的布，密度增加1倍，透气 性能减少50％。纺织品的经纬纱之间呈直通气孔的比交错排列呈斜纹气孔的透气性好，所以夏季穿密度低、散热快的服装，才觉得凉快。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-224\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/54081d19e2bf1762995969@0e_1l_4096w_4096h_90Q-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"54081d19e2bf1762995969@0e_1l_4096w_4096h_90Q\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" />\r\n(3) 覆盖性：服装的肥瘦和覆盖体表面积的大小也与散热有很大关系。“露”、“透”的夏装，当然穿着凉快。一般而言，衣服覆盖面积越小，身体散热 越快。研究测定表明，人体在裸体情况下，辐射散热要比穿着普通衣服大10倍。所以夏装宜穿短衫、短裤、短裙。在裙子中，喇叭裙、连衣裙在走动时 能产生很好的鼓风作用，因此比西服裙凉快。夏装的开口部分，敞开的比紧口的凉快得多。 但在特殊的环境下活动，覆盖体表面积大些反而觉得凉快。例如长时间在烈日下活动，或野外作业，穿着长袖衣裤既可防止强烈的阳光辐射，又显得凉 快。据说，非洲人夏季喜欢穿长袍就是这个道理。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-225\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/TB20fVfoFXXXXXCXpXXXXXXXXXX_1657497833.jpg_430x430q90-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"TB20fVfoFXXXXXCXpXXXXXXXXXX_!!1657497833.jpg_430x430q90\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n掌握这些知识，老年朋友就不用光靠自己的经验来判断夏天衣服面料是否合适自己了。增加一些科学小知识，我们的生活会更加的多姿多彩。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/7LFFO3KMHXQ5W69O.png\" alt=\"7L]FFO}3$KMH&#096;XQ5W${&#096;69O\" width=\"84\" height=\"84\" />\r\n\r\n长按上方二维码点击关注，获得更多中老年时尚服装咨询\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','学会识别服装面料 让夏季更凉快','','publish','open','open','','%e5%ad%a6%e4%bc%9a%e8%af%86%e5%88%ab%e6%9c%8d%e8%a3%85%e9%9d%a2%e6%96%99-%e8%ae%a9%e5%a4%8f%e5%ad%a3%e6%9b%b4%e5%87%89%e5%bf%ab','','','2016-05-27 10:50:18','2016-05-27 02:50:18','',0,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/?p=221',0,'post','',0),(222,3,'2016-05-27 10:45:31','2016-05-27 02:45:31','','2015032809320584','','inherit','open','closed','','2015032809320584','','','2016-05-27 10:45:31','2016-05-27 02:45:31','',221,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/2015032809320584.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(223,3,'2016-05-27 10:45:54','2016-05-27 02:45:54','','Fq6kZVPQN0SjeUtL6QQza4I3Tx-Z','','inherit','open','closed','','fq6kzvpqn0sjeutl6qqza4i3tx-z','','','2016-05-27 10:45:54','2016-05-27 02:45:54','',221,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Fq6kZVPQN0SjeUtL6QQza4I3Tx-Z.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(224,3,'2016-05-27 10:46:12','2016-05-27 02:46:12','','54081d19e2bf1762995969@0e_1l_4096w_4096h_90Q','','inherit','open','closed','','54081d19e2bf17629959690e_1l_4096w_4096h_90q','','','2016-05-27 10:46:12','2016-05-27 02:46:12','',221,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/54081d19e2bf1762995969@0e_1l_4096w_4096h_90Q.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(225,3,'2016-05-27 10:46:40','2016-05-27 02:46:40','','TB20fVfoFXXXXXCXpXXXXXXXXXX_!!1657497833.jpg_430x430q90','','inherit','open','closed','','tb20fvfofxxxxxcxpxxxxxxxxxx_1657497833-jpg_430x430q90','','','2016-05-27 10:46:40','2016-05-27 02:46:40','',221,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-conte