6Z9dWLd5IVmOfVian1OzuCbAMpzleHfp4jQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"543\" height=\"355\" /></section><section><section>\r\n<h3 class=\"color1\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\"><strong>05  固定脚垫</strong></span></h3>\r\n</section></section><section>注意门口、卫生间前和室内楼梯的脚垫，最好将脚垫固定在地面或楼梯踏板上，防止出现“卷角”情况。</section><section></section><section></section><section><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/vZNXbgjEU5wFHibXu3s9G2ahHl4x09yfNE7tH3z9zJ4CCia6FmDQN0Mad7H4M9CeJ636wkvzbxtcVXGWF5uk7bng/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"534\" height=\"534\" /></section><section><section>\r\n<h3 class=\"color1\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\"><strong>06  门窗易拉，高度适中</strong></span></h3>\r\n</section></section><section>老年人居室门窗要易开、易关。拉手选用旋转臂较长的，避免采用球形拉手，拉手高度宜在900mm到1000mm之间。根据老人的身高窗台尽量放低，最好在750mm左右。</section><section><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/vZNXbgjEU5wFHibXu3s9G2ahHl4x09yfNhnWiahiaWtuy3N0J3HsvkvCDgZtI4PwHkhl1mZ8G2lfnya4HVdZMgNqw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"549\" /></section><section><section>\r\n<h3 class=\"color1\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">07  色调沉稳</span></strong></h3>\r\n</section></section><section>从科学角度看，居室色彩与光、热的协调搭配，过于艳丽，会干扰老年人的神经系统，使人感到心烦意乱。</section><section></section><section><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/vZNXbgjEU5wFHibXu3s9G2ahHl4x09yfNP1MABTolprMJH9icMIhVYSaGrKABQ2Qglqibc0sAbyXjJbKFvmYqr15w/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"541\" height=\"541\" /></section><section><section>\r\n<h3 class=\"color1\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\"><strong>08  边角圆滑</strong></span></h3>\r\n</section></section><section>老年人如果腿脚不便，在选择卧室家具的时候，少一些棱棱角角和不必要的突出物，避免磕碰。</section><section></section><section><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/vZNXbgjEU5wFHibXu3s9G2ahHl4x09yfNpC4ick7yYicBEL0RGCFr0J5RBEUiaTjetwiaDSVW31SOJ4fWiadvZAtV9ZQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"551\" height=\"376\" /></section>','','','inherit','closed','closed','','269-revision-v1','','','2016-05-30 15:16:40','2016-05-30 07:16:40','',269,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/2016/05/30/269-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(318,4,'2016-05-30 15:17:42','2016-05-30 07:17:42','<p title=\"老人房如何装修\">老年人的居住的环境应该与老人的生理和心理特点相适应，在装修时注意以下几点，就能为他们营造出舒适优雅、简洁方便的老年居室新天地。</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">01  位置合理</span></strong></h3>\r\n<section><section><section class=\"color1\"> 老人房计置的位置很讲究。如果是别墅，老人房的位置大多都是在一楼，因为不用爬楼梯；如果是洋房，老人房应靠近厨房、生活阳台。老人房也可以与其他房间分开布置，这样生活习惯不同也不会互相影响，但是不要让老人房太孤立，方便互动，增加和睦。</section><section class=\"color1\"></section><section class=\"color1\"></section></section></section><section></section><section></section><section><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/vZNXbgjEU5wFHibXu3s9G2ahHl4x09yfNQq0KWKJ0tz2zY9wNibIuV1hiaNpicBABUbQKYc0HUtLf3WpIRVnav5pZQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"507\" height=\"380\" />                                                                                                              </section><section><section>\r\n<h3 class=\"color1\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">02  隔音要好</span></strong></h3>\r\n</section></section><section>老年人的一大特点是好静。最基本的要求是<a target=\"_blank\">门</a>窗、墙壁隔音效果要好，不受外界影响，使老人心境平和。</section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/vZNXbgjEU5xyE2lgwnAptbiaWRxvfcgYFThMMmCD8kLhB7nAEYia8ktKz4V1FvP5o3jPIBdOEpBwg5RfvRQHASsA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"534\" height=\"320\" /></section><section><section>\r\n<h3 class=\"color1\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">03  环保选材</span></strong></h3>\r\n</section></section><section>对材料选择提出了更严格的要求，如环保标准要求与学校、幼儿园一样。老人房所用的涂料、板材家具，要格外注意环保标准。</section><section></section><section></section><section><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/vZNXbgjEU5wFHibXu3s9G2ahHl4x09yfNo0zM7nmBcCkYtVU2aHARyVWLnVdER4HD69Fx6W3T5PicoicqffwAYRVQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"534\" height=\"321\" /></section><section><section>\r\n<h3 class=\"color1\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">04  地面防滑</span></strong></h3>\r\n</section></section><section><a target=\"_blank\">装饰材料</a>要符合老年人的喜好，与居室整体风格相协调，<a target=\"_blank\">地面</a>材料要求防滑。目前防滑性能好的材料主要有拼木<a target=\"_blank\">地板</a>、<a target=\"_blank\">地毯</a>、石英地板砖、凹凸条纹状的<a target=\"_blank\">地砖</a>及防滑<a target=\"_blank\">马赛克</a>等。</section><section></section><section></section><section><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/vZNXbgjEU5wFHibXu3s9G2ahHl4x09yfNhY9icWdHrpWibrPESawITh6Z9dWLd5IVmOfVian1OzuCbAMpzleHfp4jQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"543\" height=\"355\" /></section><section><section>\r\n<h3 class=\"color1\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\"><strong>05  固定脚垫</strong></span></h3>\r\n</section></section><section>注意门口、卫生间前和室内楼梯的脚垫，最好将脚垫固定在地面或楼梯踏板上，防止出现“卷角”情况。</section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/vZNXbgjEU5wFHibXu3s9G2ahHl4x09yfNE7tH3z9zJ4CCia6FmDQN0Mad7H4M9CeJ636wkvzbxtcVXGWF5uk7bng/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"534\" height=\"534\" /></section><section><section>\r\n<h3 class=\"color1\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\"><strong>06  门窗易拉，高度适中</strong></span></h3>\r\n</section></section><section>老年人居室门窗要易开、易关。拉手选用旋转臂较长的，避免采用球形拉手，拉手高度宜在900mm到1000mm之间。根据老人的身高窗台尽量放低，最好在750mm左右。</section><section></section><section><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/vZNXbgjEU5wFHibXu3s9G2ahHl4x09yfNhnWiahiaWtuy3N0J3HsvkvCDgZtI4PwHkhl1mZ8G2lfnya4HVdZMgNqw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"549\" /></section><section><section>\r\n<h3 class=\"color1\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">07  色调沉稳</span></strong></h3>\r\n</section></section><section>从科学角度看，居室色彩与光、热的协调搭配，过于艳丽，会干扰老年人的神经系统，使人感到心烦意乱。</section><section></section><section></section><section><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/vZNXbgjEU5wFHibXu3s9G2ahHl4x09yfNP1MABTolprMJH9icMIhVYSaGrKABQ2Qglqibc0sAbyXjJbKFvmYqr15w/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"541\" height=\"541\" /></section><section><section>\r\n<h3 class=\"color1\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\"><strong>08  边角圆滑</strong></span></h3>\r\n</section></section><section>老年人如果腿脚不便，在选择卧室家具的时候，少一些棱棱角角和不必要的突出物，避免磕碰。</section><section></section><section></section><section><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/vZNXbgjEU5wFHibXu3s9G2ahHl4x09yfNpC4ick7yYicBEL0RGCFr0J5RBEUiaTjetwiaDSVW31SOJ4fWiadvZAtV9ZQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"551\" height=\"376\" /></section>','老年居室装修宝典','','inherit','closed','closed','','269-revision-v1','','','2016-05-30 15:17:42','2016-05-30 07:17:42','',269,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/2016/05/30/269-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(319,4,'2016-05-30 15:19:25','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','自动草稿','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-05-30 15:19:25','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/?p=319',0,'post','',0),(320,4,'2016-05-30 15:20:30','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','自动草稿','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-05-30 15:20:30','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/?p=320',0,'post','',0),(321,4,'2016-05-30 15:44:18','2016-05-30 07:44:18','老年人的居住的环境应该与老人的生理和心理特点相适应，在装修时注意以下几点，就能为他们营造出舒适优雅、简洁方便的老年居室新天地。\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">01  位置合理</span></h2>\r\n老人房计置的位置很讲究。如果是别墅，老人房的位置大多都是在一楼，因为不用爬楼梯；如果是洋房，老人房应靠近厨房、生活阳台。老人房也可以与其他房间分开布置，这样生活习惯不同也不会互相影响，但是不要让老人房太孤立，方便互动，增加和睦。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-322 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0.jpg\" alt=\"0\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">02  隔音要好</span></h2>\r\n老年人的一大特点是好静。最基本的要求是门窗、墙壁隔音效果要好，不受外界影响，使老人心境平和。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-324\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-1-1-1024x614.jpg\" alt=\"0 (1)\" width=\"530\" height=\"318\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">03  环保选材</span></h2>\r\n对材料选择提出了更严格的要求，如环保标准要求与学校、幼儿园一样。老人房所用的涂料、板材家具，要格外注意环保标准。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-325\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-2.jpg\" alt=\"0 (2)\" width=\"504\" height=\"303\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">04  地面防滑</span></h2>\r\n装饰材料要符合老年人的喜好，与居室整体风格相协调，地面材料要求防滑。目前防滑性能好的材料主要有拼木地板、地毯、石英地板砖、凹凸条纹状的地砖及防滑马赛克等。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-326\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-3.jpg\" alt=\"0 (3)\" width=\"513\" height=\"336\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">05  固定脚垫</span></h2>\r\n注意门口、卫生间前和室内楼梯的脚垫，最好将脚垫固定在地面或楼梯踏板上，防止出现“卷角”情况。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-328\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-4-1.jpg\" alt=\"0 (4)\" width=\"514\" height=\"514\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">06  门窗易拉，高度适中</span></h2>\r\n老年人居室门窗要易开、易关。拉手选用旋转臂较长的，避免采用球形拉手，拉手高度宜在900mm到1000mm之间。根据老人的身高窗台尽量放低，最好在750mm左右。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-329\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-5.jpg\" alt=\"0 (5)\" width=\"514\" height=\"514\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">07  色调沉稳</span></h2>\r\n从科学角度看，居室色彩与光、热的协调搭配，过于艳丽，会干扰老年人的神经系统，使人感到心烦意乱。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-330\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-6.jpg\" alt=\"0 (6)\" width=\"514\" height=\"514\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">08  边角圆滑</span></h2>\r\n老年人如果腿脚不便，在选择卧室家具的时候，少一些棱棱角角和不必要的突出物，避免磕碰。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-331\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-7.jpg\" alt=\"0 (7)\" width=\"525\" height=\"358\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n1、部分图片来源于网络，版权归原作者。慧家家编撰，仅限交流学习，不做商用。\r\n\r\n2、转载请注明出处。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-332 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/qrcode_for_gh_57d2a3b1798f_258.jpg\" alt=\"qrcode_for_gh_57d2a3b1798f_258\" width=\"269\" height=\"269\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ff9900\"><strong>关心无处不在，你我的慧家家</strong></span></h2>','老年家居装修宝典','','publish','open','open','','%e8%80%81%e5%b9%b4%e5%ae%b6%e5%b1%85%e8%a3%85%e4%bf%ae%e5%ae%9d%e5%85%b8','','','2016-05-30 17:03:17','2016-05-30 09:03:17','',0,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/?p=321',0,'post','',0),(322,4,'2016-05-30 15:22:24','2016-05-30 07:22:24','','0','','inherit','open','closed','','0','','','2016-05-30 15:22:24','2016-05-30 07:22:24','',321,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(324,4,'2016-05-30 15:25:40','2016-05-30 07:25:40','','0 (1)','','inherit','open','closed','','0-1-2','','','2016-05-30 15:25:40','2016-05-30 07:25:40','',321,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-1-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(325,4,'2016-05-30 15:27:03','2016-05-30 07:27:03','','0 (2)','','inherit','open','closed','','0-2','','','2016-05-30 15:27:03','2016-05-30 07:27:03','',321,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(326,4,'2016-05-30 15:28:29','2016-05-30 07:28:29','','0 (3)','','inherit','open','closed','','0-3','','','2016-05-30 15:28:29','2016-05-30 07:28:29','',321,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(328,4,'2016-05-30 15:31:46','2016-05-30 07:31:46','','0 (4)','','inherit','open','closed','','0-4-2','','','2016-05-30 15:31:46','2016-05-30 07:31:46','',321,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-4-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(329,4,'2016-05-30 15:34:13','2016-05-30 07:34:13','','0 (5)','','inherit','open','closed','','0-5','','','2016-05-30 15:34:13','2016-05-30 07:34:13','',321,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-5.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(330,4,'2016-05-30 15:35:33','2016-05-30 07:35:33','','0 (6)','','inherit','open','closed','','0-6','','','2016-05-30 15:35:33','2016-05-30 07:35:33','',321,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-6.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(331,4,'2016-05-30 15:36:51','2016-05-30 07:36:51','','0 (7)','','inherit','open','closed','','0-7','','','2016-05-30 15:36:51','2016-05-30 07:36:51','',321,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-7.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(332,4,'2016-05-30 15:38:39','2016-05-30 07:38:39','','qrcode_for_gh_57d2a3b1798f_258','','inherit','open','closed','','qrcode_for_gh_57d2a3b1798f_258','','','2016-05-30 15:38:39','2016-05-30 07:38:39','',321,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/qrcode_for_gh_57d2a3b1798f_258.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(333,4,'2016-05-30 15:40:16','2016-05-30 07:40:16','老年人的居住的环境应该与老人的生理和心理特点相适应，在装修时注意以下几点，就能为他们营造出舒适优雅、简洁方便的老年居室新天地。\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">01  位置合理</span></h3>\r\n老人房计置的位置很讲究。如果是别墅，老人房的位置大多都是在一楼，因为不用爬楼梯；如果是洋房，老人房应靠近厨房、生活阳台。老人房也可以与其他房间分开布置，这样生活习惯不同也不会互相影响，但是不要让老人房太孤立，方便互动，增加和睦。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-322 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0.jpg\" alt=\"0\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">02  隔音要好</span></h3>\r\n老年人的一大特点是好静。最基本的要求是门窗、墙壁隔音效果要好，不受外界影响，使老人心境平和。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-324\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-1-1-1024x614.jpg\" alt=\"0 (1)\" width=\"530\" height=\"318\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">03  环保选材</span></h3>\r\n对材料选择提出了更严格的要求，如环保标准要求与学校、幼儿园一样。老人房所用的涂料、板材家具，要格外注意环保标准。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-325\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-2.jpg\" alt=\"0 (2)\" width=\"504\" height=\"303\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">04  地面防滑</span></h3>\r\n装饰材料要符合老年人的喜好，与居室整体风格相协调，地面材料要求防滑。目前防滑性能好的材料主要有拼木地板、地毯、石英地板砖、凹凸条纹状的地砖及防滑马赛克等。<img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-326\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-3.jpg\" alt=\"0 (3)\" width=\"513\" height=\"336\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">05  固定脚垫</span></h3>\r\n注意门口、卫生间前和室内楼梯的脚垫，最好将脚垫固定在地面或楼梯踏板上，防止出现“卷角”情况。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-328\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-4-1.jpg\" alt=\"0 (4)\" width=\"514\" height=\"514\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">06  门窗易拉，高度适中</span></h3>\r\n老年人居室门窗要易开、易关。拉手选用旋转臂较长的，避免采用球形拉手，拉手高度宜在900mm到1000mm之间。根据老人的身高窗台尽量放低，最好在750mm左右。<img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-329\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-5.jpg\" alt=\"0 (5)\" width=\"514\" height=\"514\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">07  色调沉稳</span></h3>\r\n从科学角度看，居室色彩与光、热的协调搭配，过于艳丽，会干扰老年人的神经系统，使人感到心烦意乱。<img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-330\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-6.jpg\" alt=\"0 (6)\" width=\"514\" height=\"514\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">08  边角圆滑</span></h3>\r\n老年人如果腿脚不便，在选择卧室家具的时候，少一些棱棱角角和不必要的突出物，避免磕碰。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-331\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-7.jpg\" alt=\"0 (7)\" width=\"525\" height=\"358\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-332 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/qrcode_for_gh_57d2a3b1798f_258.jpg\" alt=\"qrcode_for_gh_57d2a3b1798f_258\" width=\"269\" height=\"269\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ff9900\"><strong>关心不处不在，你我的慧家家</strong></span></h2>','','','inherit','closed','closed','','321-revision-v1','','','2016-05-30 15:40:16','2016-05-30 07:40:16','',321,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/2016/05/30/321-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(334,4,'2016-05-30 15:40:47','2016-05-30 07:40:47','老年人的居住的环境应该与老人的生理和心理特点相适应，在装修时注意以下几点，就能为他们营造出舒适优雅、简洁方便的老年居室新天地。\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">01  位置合理</span></h3>\r\n老人房计置的位置很讲究。如果是别墅，老人房的位置大多都是在一楼，因为不用爬楼梯；如果是洋房，老人房应靠近厨房、生活阳台。老人房也可以与其他房间分开布置，这样生活习惯不同也不会互相影响，但是不要让老人房太孤立，方便互动，增加和睦。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-322 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0.jpg\" alt=\"0\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">02  隔音要好</span></h3>\r\n老年人的一大特点是好静。最基本的要求是门窗、墙壁隔音效果要好，不受外界影响，使老人心境平和。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-324\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-1-1-1024x614.jpg\" alt=\"0 (1)\" width=\"530\" height=\"318\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">03  环保选材</span></h3>\r\n对材料选择提出了更严格的要求，如环保标准要求与学校、幼儿园一样。老人房所用的涂料、板材家具，要格外注意环保标准。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-325\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-2.jpg\" alt=\"0 (2)\" width=\"504\" height=\"303\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">04  地面防滑</span></h3>\r\n装饰材料要符合老年人的喜好，与居室整体风格相协调，地面材料要求防滑。目前防滑性能好的材料主要有拼木地板、地毯、石英地板砖、凹凸条纹状的地砖及防滑马赛克等。<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-326\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/micr