20','2016-05-30 07:56:20','','836272660866321034','','inherit','open','closed','','836272660866321034','','','2016-05-30 16:03:03','2016-05-30 08:03:03','',351,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/836272660866321034.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(346,5,'2016-05-30 15:56:21','2016-05-30 07:56:21','','854188970664939167','','inherit','open','closed','','854188970664939167','','','2016-05-30 15:56:21','2016-05-30 07:56:21','',0,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/854188970664939167.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(347,5,'2016-05-30 15:56:23','2016-05-30 07:56:23','','904523493907212162','','inherit','open','closed','','904523493907212162','','','2016-05-30 15:59:10','2016-05-30 07:59:10','',351,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/904523493907212162.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(348,5,'2016-05-30 15:57:45','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','自动草稿','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-05-30 15:57:45','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/?p=348',0,'post','',0),(349,5,'2016-05-30 15:57:53','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','自动草稿','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-05-30 15:57:53','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/?p=349',0,'post','',0),(350,5,'2016-05-30 15:58:43','2016-05-30 07:58:43','<a href=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/乐帮厨微乐乐.docx\" rel=\"\">乐帮厨</a>','','','inherit','closed','closed','','314-revision-v1','','','2016-05-30 15:58:43','2016-05-30 07:58:43','',314,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/2016/05/30/314-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(351,5,'2016-05-30 16:24:46','2016-05-30 08:24:46','<img class=\"wp-image-347 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/904523493907212162-300x195.png\" alt=\"904523493907212162\" width=\"328\" height=\"213\" />\r\n\r\n作为乐莲社区居家养老服务体系中的重要环节，乐帮厨建议老年人饮食养生应多吃“三黑”，少吃“三白”。白，即白色食物，指热量过高的肥肉、糖、盐等食物；黑，即黑色食物，有降脂、抗衰老作用的食物。<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-344 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/756245552821352863-228x300.png\" alt=\"756245552821352863\" width=\"228\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>多吃“三黑”  ：蘑菇、黑木耳、黑米</strong></p>\r\n<strong><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-339 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/165991300672789807-300x251.jpg\" alt=\"165991300672789807\" width=\"300\" height=\"251\" /></strong>蘑菇能防癌抗衰，尤其是香菇，对胆固醇有溶解作用，可降血脂、血清胆固醇，预防骨质疏松。<strong><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-340 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/216109000132404409-300x193.png\" alt=\"216109000132404409\" width=\"300\" height=\"193\" /></strong>\r\n\r\n黑木耳是天然的抗凝剂，有补血、活血、防治冠心病与动脉硬化的功效，黑木耳虽好，但也不宜多吃，每周吃两次为宜。<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-341 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/274057307830030964-300x273.jpg\" alt=\"274057307830030964\" width=\"300\" height=\"273\" />黑米外表墨黑，营养丰富，有“黑珍珠”和“世界米中之王”的美誉，尤其适合腰酸膝软、四肢乏力的老人，故黑米又有“药米”之称。将黑米熬粥容易消化吸收，还具有很好的滋补作用。\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>少吃“三白”  ：盐、糖、脂肪</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-345 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/836272660866321034-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"836272660866321034\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />吃盐过多易导致血压增高、血管硬化，还会增加肾脏的负担。一般来说，盐的每日摄入量以6克为宜。 <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-342 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/370143463698799719-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"370143463698799719\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></p>\r\n糖是人体必需的基础物质，但过量摄入容易引起高血压、肥胖、肝功能损伤等。所以要尽量少食糖分过多的食物哦。<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-343 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/675828671575115810-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"675828671575115810\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" />动物脂肪会加剧血管硬化，增加胆固醇，在此乐帮厨建议广大老年朋友们动物脂肪不可多吃，但也不能不吃。在每人每天食用油25克—30克的前提下，植物油与动物脂肪的比以10：7为宜哦。\r\n\r\n说明：\r\n\r\n1、部分来源于网络，版权归原作者。图片由乐帮厨编撰，仅限交流学习，不做商用。\r\n\r\n2、转载请注明出处。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-353\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/LBC-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"LBC\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />','老年人饮食养生应少“白”多“黑”','','publish','open','open','','%e8%80%81%e5%b9%b4%e4%ba%ba%e9%a5%ae%e9%a3%9f%e5%85%bb%e7%94%9f%e5%ba%94%e5%b0%91%e7%99%bd%e5%a4%9a%e9%bb%91','','','2016-05-30 18:24:35','2016-05-30 10:24:35','',0,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/?p=351',0,'post','',0),(352,5,'2016-05-30 16:24:11','2016-05-30 08:24:11','<img class=\"wp-image-347 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/904523493907212162-300x195.png\" alt=\"904523493907212162\" width=\"328\" height=\"213\" />\r\n\r\n作为乐莲社区居家养老服务体系中的重要环节，乐帮厨建议老年人饮食养生应多吃“三黑”，少吃“三白”。白，即白色食物，指热量过高的肥肉、糖、盐等食物；黑，即黑色食物，有降脂、抗衰老作用的食物。<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-344 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/756245552821352863-228x300.png\" alt=\"756245552821352863\" width=\"228\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>多吃“三黑”  ：蘑菇、黑木耳、黑米</strong></p>\r\n<strong><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-339 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/165991300672789807-300x251.jpg\" alt=\"165991300672789807\" width=\"300\" height=\"251\" /></strong>蘑菇能防癌抗衰，尤其是香菇，对胆固醇有溶解作用，可降血脂、血清胆固醇，预防骨质疏松。<strong><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-340 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/216109000132404409-300x193.png\" alt=\"216109000132404409\" width=\"300\" height=\"193\" /></strong>\r\n\r\n黑木耳是天然的抗凝剂，有补血、活血、防治冠心病与动脉硬化的功效，黑木耳虽好，但也不宜多吃，每周吃两次为宜。<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-341 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/274057307830030964-300x273.jpg\" alt=\"274057307830030964\" width=\"300\" height=\"273\" />黑米外表墨黑，营养丰富，有“黑珍珠”和“世界米中之王”的美誉，尤其适合腰酸膝软、四肢乏力的老人，故黑米又有“药米”之称。将黑米熬粥容易消化吸收，还具有很好的滋补作用。\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>少吃“三白”  ：盐、糖、脂肪</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-345 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/836272660866321034-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"836272660866321034\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />吃盐过多易导致血压增高、血管硬化，还会增加肾脏的负担。一般来说，盐的每日摄入量以6克为宜。 <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-342 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/370143463698799719-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"370143463698799719\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></p>\r\n糖是人体必需的基础物质，但过量摄入容易引起高血压、肥胖、肝功能损伤等。所以要尽量少食糖分过多的食物哦。<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-343 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/675828671575115810-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"675828671575115810\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" />动物脂肪会加剧血管硬化，增加胆固醇，在此乐帮厨建议广大老年朋友们动物脂肪不可多吃，但也不能不吃。在每人每天食用油25克—30克的前提下，植物油与动物脂肪的比以10：7为宜哦。\r\n\r\n说明：\r\n\r\n1、部分来源于网络，版权归原作者。图片由乐帮厨编撰，仅限交流学习，不做商用。\r\n\r\n2、转载请注明出处。','老年人饮食养生应少“白”多“黑”','','inherit','closed','closed','','351-revision-v1','','','2016-05-30 16:24:11','2016-05-30 08:24:11','',351,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/2016/05/30/351-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(353,5,'2016-05-30 16:29:45','2016-05-30 08:29:45','','LBC','','inherit','open','closed','','lbc','','','2016-05-30 16:32:21','2016-05-30 08:32:21','',351,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/LBC.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(354,5,'2016-05-30 16:32:36','2016-05-30 08:32:36','<img class=\"wp-image-347 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/904523493907212162-300x195.png\" alt=\"904523493907212162\" width=\"328\" height=\"213\" />\r\n\r\n作为乐莲社区居家养老服务体系中的重要环节，乐帮厨建议老年人饮食养生应多吃“三黑”，少吃“三白”。白，即白色食物，指热量过高的肥肉、糖、盐等食物；黑，即黑色食物，有降脂、抗衰老作用的食物。<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-344 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/756245552821352863-228x300.png\" alt=\"756245552821352863\" width=\"228\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>多吃“三黑”  ：蘑菇、黑木耳、黑米</strong></p>\r\n<strong><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-339 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/165991300672789807-300x251.jpg\" alt=\"165991300672789807\" width=\"300\" height=\"251\" /></strong>蘑菇能防癌抗衰，尤其是香菇，对胆固醇有溶解作用，可降血脂、血清胆固醇，预防骨质疏松。<strong><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-340 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/216109000132404409-300x193.png\" alt=\"216109000132404409\" width=\"300\" height=\"193\" /></strong>\r\n\r\n黑木耳是天然的抗凝剂，有补血、活血、防治冠心病与动脉硬化的功效，黑木耳虽好，但也不宜多吃，每周吃两次为宜。<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-341 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/274057307830030964-300x273.jpg\" alt=\"274057307830030964\" width=\"300\" height=\"273\" />黑米外表墨黑，营养丰富，有“黑珍珠”和“世界米中之王”的美誉，尤其适合腰酸膝软、四肢乏力的老人，故黑米又有“药米”之称。将黑米熬粥容易消化吸收，还具有很好的滋补作用。\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>少吃“三白”  ：盐、糖、脂肪</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-345 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/836272660866321034-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"836272660866321034\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />吃盐过多易导致血压增高、血管硬化，还会增加肾脏的负担。一般来说，盐的每日摄入量以6克为宜。 <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-342 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/370143463698799719-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"370143463698799719\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></p>\r\n糖是人体必需的基础物质，但过量摄入容易引起高血压、肥胖、肝功能损伤等。所以要尽量少食糖分过多的食物哦。<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-343 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/675828671575115810-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"675828671575115810\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" />动物脂肪会加剧血管硬化，增加胆固醇，在此乐帮厨建议广大老年朋友们动物脂肪不可多吃，但也不能不吃。在每人每天食用油25克—30克的前提下，植物油与动物脂肪的比以10：7为宜哦。\r\n\r\n说明：\r\n\r\n1、部分来源于网络，版权归原作者。图片由乐帮厨编撰，仅限交流学习，不做商用。\r\n\r\n2、转载请注明出处。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-353\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/LBC-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"LBC\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />','老年人饮食养生应少“白”多“黑”','','inherit','closed','closed','','351-revision-v1','','','2016-05-30 16:32:36','2016-05-30 08:32:36','',351,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/2016/05/30/351-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(355,4,'2016-05-30 17:03:17','2016-05-30 09:03:17','老年人的居住的环境应该与老人的生理和心理特点相适应，在装修时注意以下几点，就能为他们营造出舒适优雅、简洁方便的老年居室新天地。\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">01  位置合理</span></h2>\r\n老人房计置的位置很讲究。如果是别墅，老人房的位置大多都是在一楼，因为不用爬楼梯；如果是洋房，老人房应靠近厨房、生活阳台。老人房也可以与其他房间分开布置，这样生活习惯不同也不会互相影响，但是不要让老人房太孤立，方便互动，增加和睦。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-322 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0.jpg\" alt=\"0\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">02  隔音要好</span></h2>\r\n老年人的一大特点是好静。最基本的要求是门窗、墙壁隔音效果要好，不受外界影响，使老人心境平和。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-324\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-1-1-1024x614.jpg\" alt=\"0 (1)\" width=\"530\" height=\"318\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">03  环保选材</span></h2>\r\n对材料选择提出了更严格的要求，如环保标准要求与学校、幼儿园一样。老人房所用的涂料、板材家具，要格外注意环保标准。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-325\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-2.jpg\" alt=\"0 (2)\" width=\"504\" height=\"303\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">04  地面防滑</span></h2>\r\n装饰材料要符合老年人的喜好，与居室整体风格相协调，地面材料要求防滑。目前防滑性能好的材料主要有拼木地板、地毯、石英地板砖、凹凸条纹状的地砖及防滑马赛克等。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-326\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-3.jpg\" alt=\"0 (3)\" width=\"513\" height=\"336\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">05  固定脚垫</span></h2>\r\n注意门口、卫生间前和室内楼梯的脚垫，最好将脚垫固定在地面或楼梯踏板上，防止出现“卷角”情况。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-328\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-4-1.jpg\" alt=\"0 (4)\" width=\"514\" height=\"514\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">06  门窗易拉，高度适中</span></h2>\r\n老年人居室门窗要易开、易关。拉手选用旋转臂较长的，避免采用球形拉手，拉手高度宜在900mm到1000mm之间。根据老人的身高窗台尽量放低，最好在750mm左右。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-329\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-5.jpg\" alt=\"0 (5)\" width=\"514\" height=\"514\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">07  色调沉稳</span></h2>\r\n从科学角度看，居室色彩与光、热的协调搭配，过于艳丽，会干扰老年人的神经系统，使人感到心烦意乱。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-330\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-6.jpg\" alt=\"0 (6)\" width=\"514\" height=\"514\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff\">08  边角圆滑</span></h2>\r\n老年人如果腿脚不便，在选择卧室家具的时候，少一些棱棱角角和不必要的突出物，避免磕碰。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-331\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/0-7.jpg\" alt=\"0 (7)\" width=\"525\" height=\"358\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n1、部分图片来源于网络，版权归原作者。慧家家编撰，仅限交流学习，不做商用。\r\n\r\n2、转载请注明出处。\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-332 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.microlele.com/microlele/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/qrcode_for_gh_57d2a3b1798f_258.jpg\" alt=\"qrcode_for_gh_57d2a3b1798f_258\" width=\"269\" height=\"269\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ff9900\"><strong>关心无处不在，你我的慧家家</strong></span></h2>','老年家居装修宝典','','inherit','closed','closed','','321-revision-v1','','','2016-05-30 17:03:17','2016-05-30 09:03:17','',321,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/2016/05/30/321-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(356,10,'2016-05-30 18:18:29','2016-05-30 10:18:29','<div>\r\n<div id=\"vpofficialtitlev5_wrap\">\r\n<div id=\"vpofficialtitlev5\">\r\n<div class=\"base\">\r\n<div class=\"base_info\">\r\n<div class=\"guide\">\r\n<div class=\"crumbs\"><span id=\"subtitle\" title=\"小吴哥日出 01\">小吴哥日出 01</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"ab_pip\" class=\"ad_area\">\r\n<div id=\"ab_v_324\">\r\n<div id=\"youku_ad_crazy\" class=\"mod\" align=\"center\"><iframe id=\"9725a54c\" src=\"http://cas.sh.cn.criteo.com/delivery/r/afr.php?did=574c13578bcd0d765054a6f9f793a4a0&amp;z=ADcTu3bwueLEjXtWGkB4abuRUtvSYraZpZotBPugVUU&amp;u=%7CcTEQUI%2BclNCp7yyDBXrfSLyiWG0FrHcJZKHwHTrWtZw%3D%7C&amp;c1=4z_1vBnVXyU3s5S1ODdcxBEhMh_1PE6dCt88-QtmDLEx3ip1dXueLubIW9w5cAUlW-y5Nu4_wekAR_6eTVTI8QB9_9bShfGSVXoGWXQ1ZymhVQ0Yv6DfMsdVSFG07mfUPmmG65vmMAKgYQKlKbijHlPa9KJ0Auo9BaGWOebCzQNcX09rGSTGsFB4a4BgRdNZwjR9lFrFrzH4FRJ6OBvMtyAhbpR0x0hL5pX1p1XPhgc&amp;ct0=http%3A%2F%2Fm.yes.youku.com%2Fbc.gif%3F1926%26lu%3D%26ui%3D1461204488165Uv1%26hi%3D%26vi%3D322884081%26oi%3D787162152%26pi%3D303485%26cai%3Dpker%26sci%3D%26ct%3Dw%26st%3DWindows%26dt%3D2%26an%3D%26vvi%3D1464603468279Amx26d%26si%3D3%26mi%3D3%26ri%3Da15-0V7M-02eppO-0HS-0i7%26imi%3D075df57138129bfbb03a62df31923fe3%26ap%3D75%26wd%3D%26tn%3D%26ai%3D%26idi%3D0%26cri%3D6294648%26wp%3D31%26bp%3D30%26wds%3D11164%26wbi%3D1%26vt%3D0%26pt%3D%26vl%3D0%26u%3D\" name=\"9725a54c\" width=\"300\" height=\"50\" frameborder=\"no\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"playBox\" class=\"play_area\">\r\n<div id=\"playerBox\" class=\"playBox\">\r\n<div class=\"playArea\">\r\n<div class=\"abs\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"player\" class=\"player\"><object id=\"movie_player\" data=\"http://static.youku.com/v1.0.0625/v/swf/loader.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\"></object></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"player_sidebar\" class=\"listBox\">\r\n<div class=\"listSkip\">\r\n<div id=\"listareashow\" class=\"listArea\">\r\n<div class=\"show_tab\">\r\n<div class=\"tabs\">\r\n<ul id=\"DramaTab\">\r\n	<li class=\"current\"></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"window\"></div>','测试','','trash','open','open','','%e6%b5%8b%e8%af%95','','','2016-05-30 18:23:50','2016-05-30 10:23:50','',0,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/?p=356',0,'post','',0),(357,10,'2016-05-30 18:18:29','2016-05-30 10:18:29','[embed]http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTI5MTUzNjMyNA==.html?refer=pc-sns-1[/embed]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n学习一下','测试','','inherit','closed','closed','','356-revision-v1','','','2016-05-30 18:18:29','2016-05-30 10:18:29','',356,'http://www.microlele.com/microlele/2016/05/30/356-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(358,10,'2016-05-30 18:19:47','2016-05-30 10:19:47','<div><object id=\"MTIOTV39AL1HP10K\" data=\"http://irs01.net/MTFlashStore.swf#\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\"></object></div>\n<div class=\"window\">\n<div class=\"screen\">\n<div class=\"s_body\">\n<div id=\"dfmaxthonv5_wrap\"></div>\n<div id=\"copyright_tips\"></div>\n<div id=\"qheader\" class=\"yk-header yk-header-fixed\">\n<div id=\"qheader_box\" class=\"yk-header-container\">\n<div class=\"yk-box\">\n<div class=\"yk-logo\"><a title=\"Youku 优酷\" href=\"http://www.youku.com/\"><img src=\"http://static.youku.com/index/img/header/yklogo.png\" alt=\"Youku 优酷\" /></a></div>\n<div class=\"yk-so\">\n<div class=\"yk-so-box\"><form id=\"qheader_search\" action=\"http://www.soku.com/search_video\" method=\"get\" target=\"_blank\"><input id=\"headq\" class=\"default\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"q\" type=\"text\" /><i></i><button type=\"submit\"></button>\n<div></div>\n</form></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"yk-ucenter\">\n<div id=\"qheader_userlog\" class=\"yk-userlog\">\n<div id=\"qheader_logbefore\" class=\"yk-userlog-befor